overview:
What’s the best way to invoice my new client? How do I share documents? What about backing up my files? Your not alone. All entrepreneurs and small business startups ask the same questions… and more. We’re here to help you with the “How do I…?” question when it comes to your startup.

That’s why we started HeadStartUp.com.

As a group of serial entrepreneurs, we’ve asked ourselves these very questions (and a whole lot more) quite a bit. Suppose you could say we’ve been there and done that. A lot. And we actually obsess over the latest and greatest tools for small business and startups. Seriously. We have quite literally searched, used and evaluated thousands of companies so you don’t have to.

HeadStartUp is the largest database of really effective web-based tools and resources to help you get your small business startup up and running, fast. Our database is easily searchable by keyword, by category, tags, and also popularity. All to save you time and help you focus on what matters most - making your small business or startup a success.

HeadStartUp is the largest database of useful tools and resources for small business startups and entrepreneurs.
